CompanyDescription.label: Company Description
CompanyDescription.value: Caravelle International Group, through its subsidiaries, provides ocean transportation services in Singapore and internationally. The company provides international shipping services and carbon-neutral solutions for wood desiccation and carbon neutrality industry. It also provides seaborne transportation services under the voyage contracts. In addition, it provides vessel leasing and management services on behalf of ship owners. The company was founded in 2021 and is headquartered in Singapore.
